name: A test for setting a single value in a field
description:
The test sets one value in the field, then checks the list with the expected value.
To run manually copy: 'application.Samples.Form.MultiValueOnFormTest#test_once' to 'include PATH' of 'Run Workflow' button at https://github.com/CX-Box/cxbox-code-samples/actions/workflows/build_button_qa.yml
